<h1>America Under the Gun</h1>
<h2>A 50-State Analysis of Gun Violence and Its Link to Weak State Gun Laws</h2><img src="/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/AmericaUnderTheGunCOVERART-01.jpg" alt="America Under the Gun Cover Art" class="mainphoto"><p class="photosource">SOURCE: CAP Illustration/iStock</p><p class="photocaption">Many of the states with the weakest gun laws also have the highest levels of gun violence.</p><p class="byline">By <a href="/about/staff/gerney-arkadi/bio/">Arkadi Gerney</a>, <a href="/about/staff/parsons-chelsea/bio/">Chelsea Parsons</a>,  and <a href="/about/staff/posner-charles/bio/">Charles Posner</a> | <span class="timestamp">April 2, 2013</span></p>
<ul class="storytools">
<span class="no-mobile">PRINT: 
<li class="print"><a href="#" onClick="window.print();return false;"><img src="http://www.americanprogress.org/wp-content/themes/c3/images/print24.png" width="24" height="24" alt="print icon"></a></li></span>
